Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個機關會吸收智世多餘的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到了早上就會綻開結晶的花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然看起來很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明跟我們很像 看起來卻很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 還有那些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}林德爾送了龍褪下的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魚是西魯基送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賽門送了手錶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡是送了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她做得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 借我一下你在蟻冢拿到的魔繩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就會將製造吸收魔力的能力降到接近零
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很適合你的身體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽好了 不要擅自實驗和施放魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在幾乎什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明收下了許多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但無法做任何回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然身體還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我願意做任何去行動就能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 我去跟賽門先生道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也跟你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是你又偷偷去倫敦怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會再瞞著你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這很難說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真難得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都沒有人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為是聖誕節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問你有看到過一個小男孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前有看過她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道 她突然說弟弟不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們家就只有她一個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}求求你幫忙找我的弟弟 伊森吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫史黛拉‧巴克雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趁聖誕假期來外婆家過節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟家人一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我帶伊森去了後園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他身體明明很虛弱 但就是都不回屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之後我們吵了架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不想要你這種任性的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說了 伊森消失我也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伊森是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有我一個記得弟弟 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突然忘記自己的小孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你願意付出什麼代價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}代價？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們在幫助人的時候 會收下對等的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你會為我們做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}點心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來這裡的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每個月最少會來這裡一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會做很多很多點心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你抱都抱不完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想要錢的話 我會打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算花上一輩子也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是代價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是唷 他是魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魔法使？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也是魔法使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很害怕吧 發生了這麼多怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然覺得可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這些事都沒有弟弟回不來可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}狗說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從這裡消失的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分散開會很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不要跟丟任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼 真美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿著這個就不怕走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲能找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會小心拿好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有人在妨礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}問問這附近的鄰居好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是不知道它們會不會說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你遇到麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夜之愛子是蜂后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蜂后能產卵 所以受其他蜂照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是魔法 所以沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以交涉方法來說還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請告訴我這孩子的弟弟在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事 你在和誰說話呀 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉不用在意 會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道 我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕 已經沒有花了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 讓她講詳細點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半茶杯的量 不許再多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 你怎麼流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 你不用擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋 我當然會擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你都做了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她在支付代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們不是魔法使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不需要搞到自己受傷 應該也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們並不是萬能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我以前也有一個弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但已經再也見不到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想讓史黛拉能再見到你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在只能用這種方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 嚇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很期待你的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回去要立刻包紮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 智世 讓你做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我自己說要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑到這麼遠的地方 辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}灰眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個小孩被人拋棄在雪地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還回來 他是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這話說得真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拋棄他的人 不就是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們會仔細聽人們說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}語言和文字是凝聚靈魂的聲與形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一旦傳達給別人 就再也不能收回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不想要你這種任性的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是真心那麼說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你根本不知道你的話會招致什麼後果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幸好你沒有要他去死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你和你弟弟的緣分已經斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在 他的前任姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你能想起你弟弟的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉 是叫{\bord0\blur10}伊森{\r\blur5}吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼 我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}緣分已斷就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}名字 年齡 出生地 長相 聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就連他的存在都會被忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他已經屬於我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你支付得起這代價嗎 一無所有的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不要來玩一個遊戲 一無所有的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也一起吧 影之子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:13:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們兩個人去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時限就到日落為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那之前能找到他們的話 就算你們贏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輸了的話 他們就屬於我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這對我們不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你什麼也不會失去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你太自私妄為了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你那野獸的鼻子 拼命地尋找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}冬天的白晝可是很短的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦 我真的會把他忘記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要找到就行了吧 找到就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遠東的你和西方的他都能夠相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這麼小的山丘上 怎麼可能見不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也是當姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要相信你和你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然想念到會失聲痛哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們的緣分就沒那麼容易被切斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管是家人還是什麼 都一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 一起去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 你能聞得出氣味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能被藏起來了 氣味非常淡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你那野獸的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 你照顧下史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 用那個沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經認定自己的歸宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被困住了 幾乎動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那種老東西力量太強大 真是頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是智世現在用魔法就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可真像你姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你認識我姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是骷髏頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:16:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}戴著頭骨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以取下來嗎 還是天生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會應付小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.38,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變成人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你能想起姐姐的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦 不記得了 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說過吧 「我不要囉嗦的姐姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的不要了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真覺得家人不寶貴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這又不是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為那樣很丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是很懂家人或夫婦的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我有血親 是不是就能理解這種情感了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我從來沒想過血緣關係的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算沒有血緣關係 家人就是家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是長期一同生活 互相幫助的群體單位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣說的 好像什麼人都能當家人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許 我現在超想和姐姐道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也想要一起參加派對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不想和姐姐之外的人參加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為是家人 我才會這麼去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑起來 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用鼻子 聞出氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}屬於我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你為什麼變成我的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小孩子的好奇心太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我回家 聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不想要我這樣的弟弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不想我當你的姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望我的弟弟就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再說了 我也就認識你這個弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也覺得 你當我姐姐就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該說「想要你當我姐姐」 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想起名字了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好神奇 衣服居然沒有濕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法叫名字真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是場愉悅的敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是相當愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能欣賞他人認真的樣子真是愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人的話語很有分量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因此我們會時常在人類身旁靜聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽著 一無所有的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被切斷的緣分 我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還是有一樣東西的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個東西似乎更美味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還給你們好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被愚弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉 伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 你們跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她叫智世 是我今天交到的新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太謝謝你了 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告訴我 你住哪裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會守約去你家的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉可是很固執的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說什麼啦
Comment: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:32.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:37.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:47.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:57.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:04.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ合う　闇と光が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:10.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}二つの対なるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:12.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創られてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:16.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この世の総べては
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:23.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あなたがいるから私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.52,0:23:29.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}離れてもそばにいる（そばにいる）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:35.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}誰もが自分の　もう一つの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:41.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}片割れという　大切なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:49.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}探し続けてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:32.94,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}望著月亮 殘缺的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:37.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:47.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}選擇了遠路 並肩啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:57.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:04.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相互追趕的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:10.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}對立的兩種存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:12.82,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:16.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世間的芳華絢爛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:23.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只有你在 才有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.52,0:23:29.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們形影不離（形影不離）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:35.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}夢寐以求的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:41.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}屬於我們的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:49.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}我們卻仍在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:23:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一次交到朋友 少女內心歡欣雀躍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而 因為交到了這個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少女和魔法使之間的關係 產生了一點扭曲
